== Welcome to the Automatic Telescope Control System: Stargazer

This is the web application that allows users to remotely schedule telescope positions.

== Gems Used:
# for authentication/login subsystem:
install authlogic

# for time validation:
validates_timeliness

# Ffor automatically creating class diagrams from Rails applications:
railroad

# for adding text field inputs for date/time
chronic_duration

# for adding binary images to a model
paperclip

# astronomy picture of the day
dougsko-apod

# for setting cron jobs
whenever